underlying_goal: Merge a remote Git branch from Overleaf, resolving any conflicts.
primary_success: Successfully merging a remote branch with three separate conflicts, correctly choosing the remote 'Overleaf' version for all of them as intended.
brief_summary: The user instructed the agent to merge a remote git branch. The agent identified and resolved three separate merge conflicts by taking the remote (Overleaf) version for each, then committed and pushed the final result.
